---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-warm-50 border-t border-warm-200/60 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-end gap-6 mb-14 scroll-reveal">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-flame/70 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-3">
          Vecinos que encontraron su gasista
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-display font-800 text-dark text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl tracking-tight leading-tight">
          Lo que dicen<br/>los clientes.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-shrink-0 self-end pb-1 hidden sm:block" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="72" height="56" viewBox="0 0 72 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path
            d="M0 56V33.6C0 24.4 2.05333 16.8 6.16 10.8C10.2667 4.6 16.2133 1.33333 24 0.8L26.4 6.4C21.0667 7.6 16.8 10.4 13.6 14.8C10.4 19.2 8.8 24.2667 8.8 30H20.8V56H0ZM41.6 56V33.6C41.6 24.4 43.6533 16.8 47.76 10.8C51.8667 4.6 57.8133 1.33333 65.6 0.8L68 6.4C62.6667 7.6 58.4 10.4 55.2 14.8C52 19.2 50.4 24.2667 50.4 30H62.4V56H41.6Z"
            fill="#e07418"
            opacity="0.12"
          />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <article class="relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border bg-white border-warm-200/70 p-8">
        <div class="absolute top-5 right-5 font-display font-800 text-7xl leading-none select-none pointer-events-none text-warm-100" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
        <p class="text-warm-900/50 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 relative z-10 italic">
          Estamos recolectando reseñas verificadas de clientes reales. Próximamente vas a poder leer experiencias de vecinos que contrataron gasistas a través del directorio.
        </p>
        <footer class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-4 border-t border-warm-100">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-warm-100 border border-warm-200 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" class="text-warm-400">
              <circle cx="7" cy="5" r="2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/>
              <path d="M2 12C2 9.791 4.239 8 7 8C9.761 8 12 9.791 12 12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-warm-800/40 italic">Testimonios próximamente</p>
        </footer>
      </article>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
